  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为L++蓝图差异合并系统画一个状态图。核心场景是：用户先加载左右两个版本，然后进行diff，再处理可能的合并冲突。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "idle",
        "left_loaded",
        "ready",
        "diffing",
        "diff_complete",
        "merging",
        "merge_complete",
        "conflict"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。系统启动后应该有个初始状态，我理解为idle空闲态。用户需要分两步加载左右版本，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "idle",
        "left_loaded",
        "ready",
        "LOAD_LEFT",
        "LOAD_RIGHT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，先LOAD_LEFT进入left_loaded，再LOAD_RIGHT进入ready。ready态之后可以反复重新加载base、left或right，不影响当前状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "left_loaded",
        "ready",
        "LOAD_BASE",
        "LOAD_LEFT",
        "LOAD_RIGHT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把ready的自循环加上。现在从ready出发，DIFF事件会触发diffing状态，这个需要关联Retail_PointOfSale吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ready",
        "diffing",
        "DIFF",
        "Retail_PointOfSale"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，DIFF操作由Retail_PointOfSale触发，完成后进入diff_complete。另外还有个DIFF_ALL，由Retail_OrderManagement触发，可以直接从ready跳到diff_complete。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ready",
        "diff_complete",
        "DIFF_ALL",
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "diffing",
        "DIFF_DONE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加。在diff_complete状态下，用户应该能查看差异结果吧？比如summary、unified view和patch格式？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "diff_complete",
        "SHOW_SUMMARY",
        "SHOW_UNIFIED",
        "SHOW_PATCH"
