      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "从diff_complete可以进入合并流程，MERGE事件由Retail_CustomerLoyalty触发，进入merging状态。这里会分叉吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
