    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的。另外diff_complete本身也可以直接MERGE_LEFT或MERGE_RIGHT，跳过merging状态。MERGE_LEFT由Retail_CouponSystem触发，MERGE_RIGHT由Retail_PointOfSale触发。",
      "elements_involved": [
