      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这样设计很灵活。merge_complete之后可以EXPORT，由Retail_OrderManagement触发。用户还能返回diff_complete继续调整吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "merge_complete",
        "EXPORT",
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "diff_complete"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，merge_complete有BACK回到diff_complete。conflict状态也有BACK回到diff_complete，让用户重新查看差异再决定。",
