      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "图已经画完了。我检查一下：从Retail_CouponSystem进入idle，经过left_loaded到ready，支持diffing和diff_complete，merging有自动合并和冲突分支，merge_complete可以导出。",
